cross: Rhyncholaeliocattleya Chinese Bronze x Cattlya aclandiae

measurements.description: Eighteen flowers on four upright 14.5-cm inflorescences; sepals and petals dark green fully flushed red-bronze, speckled dark purple, more concentrated distally, petals very slightly ruffled; lip white, midlobe bright fucshia; column white, lightly flushed fuchsia, anther cap white; substance firm; texture glossy, lip diamond dust; commended for improvement in color and lip.
